  "title" : "Why is my project controller doesn&#39;t see my templates views?",
  "body" : "<p>I started new project with spring boot starter web and ran into a problem.</p>\n<pre><code>package com.example.project2;\n\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Controller;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.GetMapping;\nimport org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RequestMapping;\n\n@Controller\n@RequestMapping(&quot;/test&quot;)\npublic class Controller2 {\n\n    @GetMapping\n    public String indexForExample() {\n        return &quot;index&quot;;\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>index - are the file in templates directory. I double check my ways in project.</p>\n<p>All seems clear and fine.</p>\n<p>But as soon as I started, spring ( or maybe other thing ) cant find my views.<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/vTIH7T5o.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">enter image description here</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/6AQlbOBM.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">enter image description here</a></p>\n<p>Controller in package</p>\n<pre><code>package com.example.project2;\n</code></pre>\n<p>application properties -</p>\n<pre><code>spring.application.name=project2\n</code></pre>\n"
